		en: "You decide the best course of action is to smash the lock open.<br>...<br><br>Pass with a result >15: You smash the lock with ease, its remains drop to the floor. You then open the box. Inside you find a bottle labeled Sickle Pheromone.<br>...<br><br>Pass with a result <15: With maybe a little too much strength you smash the lock, but when you do you hear a smashing sound coming from within the box while a pungent odour pours from the box and fills the cave.<br>...<br><br>Fail: You clumsily drop the box and hear a smash. Whatever was in the box sure stank and is definitely gone now."
